當地時間2014年12月28日清晨05:35，亞洲航空公司8501號班機於印尼朱安達國際機場起飛，啟程前住[[新加坡樟宜机场|新加坡樟宜機場]]。據印尼飛航當局AirNav表示，航班起飛前，機師曾提升飛行高度以避開暴風雨，但因航道交通壅塞而被拒絕<ref name="af12300435">{{Cite news|url=https://hk.news.yahoo.com/亞洲航空8501-最後通訊曝光-043502021.html|title=亞洲航空8501 最後通訊曝光|language=zh-hk|publisher=法新社|date=2014-12-30|accessdate=2022-02-20|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030204413/https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA8501-%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-043502021.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。期後於航班飛行期間，機師提出要求向左轉以避過雷暴，並即時獲得批准<ref name="st12300632">{{Cite news|url=https://hk.news.yahoo.com/機長曾兩度要求改航道-063200157.html|title=機長曾兩度要求改航道|publisher=星島日報|language=zh-hk|date=2014-12-30|accessdate=2021-08-18|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030200424/https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A9%9F%E9%95%B7%E6%9B%BE%E5%85%A9%E5%BA%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%94%B9%E8%88%AA%E9%81%93-063200157.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，於是飛機改變航道向左轉了約11公里。接着，機師再次重申原本的請求，要求准許飛機爬升高度以避開惡劣天氣<ref name="st12300632" /><ref name="af12300435" />。及後於06:14，控制塔人員通知機長因上方有其他飛機，只可飛行到3萬4千呎時，飛機方面就已經沒有回應<ref name="st12300632" />，與雅加達空中管制失去聯絡。在失去聯繫之時，航機仍處於印尼管制範圍內<ref>{{cite news |language = zh-hk |url = https://hk.news.yahoo.com/亞航稱失聯客機機長以天氣惡劣要求更改航道-071400107.html |title = 亞航稱失聯客機機長以天氣惡劣要求更改航道 |publisher = 香港電台 |date = 2014-12-28 |accessdate = 2014-12-29 |archive-date = 2020-10-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201030201620/https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%9E%E8%88%AA%E7%A8%B1%E5%A4%B1%E8%81%AF%E5%AE%A2%E6%A9%9F%E6%A9%9F%E9%95%B7%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%A3%E6%83%A1%E5%8A%A3%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9%E8%88%AA%E9%81%93-071400107.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>，估計正在飛越爪哇海加里曼丹和爪哇島之間的風暴群<ref>{{cite web|title=AirAsia Flight 8501:Preliminary meteorological analysis - Weather Graphics|url=http://www.weathergraphics.com/awq8501/|website=Weather Graphics|accessdate=2014-12-28|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212110610/http://www.weathergraphics.com/awq8501/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並有着正常的[[巡航|巡航]]高度及速度<ref>{{cite web|title=AirAsia (Indonesia) Flight QZ8501 Incident|url=http://www.transportmalaysia.com/news/2014/12/28/airasia-indonesia-flight-qz8501-incident/|publisher=Transportmalaysia|accessdate=2014-12-28|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141228070748/http://www.transportmalaysia.com/news/2014/12/28/airasia-indonesia-flight-qz8501-incident/|archivedate=2014-12-28}}</ref>。

