<ref name="ibtimes-41382-20141230">亞航客機失聯最新消息：客機殘骸被找到，[http://www.ibtimes.com.cn/trad/articles/41382/20141230/air-asia-qz8501-update.htm {{zh-hant}}] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ibtimes.com.cn/trad/articles/41382/20141230/air-asia-qz8501-update.htm |date=20141231064214 }}、[http://www.ibtimes.com.cn/articles/41382/20141230/air-asia-qz8501-update.htm {{zh-cn}}] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ibtimes.com.cn/articles/41382/20141230/air-asia-qz8501-update.htm |date=20141231064202 }}，IBTimes中文網，[[国际财经时报|国际财经时报]]，2014-12-30</ref>}}，其中6,100小時在亞航飛行，副機長在亞航共有2,275小时的飛行經驗<ref>{{cite news|title=亚洲航空印尼泗水飞新加坡客机失联|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2014/12/141228_indonesia_plane|publisher=[[BBC中文網|BBC中文網]]|date=2014-12-28|accessdate=2014-12-28|archive-date=2014-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141231103617/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2014/12/141228_indonesia_plane|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/notes/airasia/updated-statement-qz8501/10152667884908742|title=Air Asia updated statemen|language=en|accessdate=2014-12-28|archive-date=2014-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141230072214/https://www.facebook.com/notes/airasia/updated-statement-qz8501/10152667884908742|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="bbc-141229_indonesia_airasia_search"/>。

